&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;i>Taking documents offline&lt;/i> (Index: offline authoring &amp;gt; taking documents offline)&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;i>Bringing offline documents back online&lt;/i> (Index: offline authoring &amp;gt; bringing documents back online)&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&lt;br />&#xD;
